00:32:30,780 --> 00:32:34,020
 hipermodularne strukture,

653
00:32:34,020 --> 00:32:37,960
 modularne strukture ukrajinskih snaga

654
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:40,240
 u hiperlealno vremenu,

655
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:43,160
 na hiperintegriranom bojištu,

656
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:45,460
 uz uporabu umjetne inteligencije,

657
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,880
 mogu u što kraće vremena,

658
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:49,300
 a to je po njihom bilo

659
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:50,640
 koliko mogu isčitati,

660
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:53,280
 jer se radi o fraktalno geometriji,

661
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:55,240
 a kao planir operacije Luja,

662
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:57,340
 fraktalna geometrija je primijenjena

663
00:32:57,340 --> 00:32:58,640
 u toj operaciji,

664
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,480
 zato Luja tako bila uspješna.

665
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:02,500
 Tamo je primijenjena još i teorija

666
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:04,760
 Igara i teorija Skupova.

667
00:33:04,760 --> 00:33:07,060
 Ovdje je nešto slično,

668
00:33:07,060 --> 00:33:09,120
 ali ovdje se radi o fraktalno geometriji,

669
00:33:09,120 --> 00:33:10,960
 znači da će doći do sedam dana

670
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:14,000
 do nukralne elektrane Kursk.

671
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,300
 Kursk, da.

672
00:33:15,820 --> 00:33:16,680
 koja je udaljena

673
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:20,460
 70 km od ukrajinske granice

674
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:22,960
 i da će to za sedam dana doći.

675
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:28,880
 I onda ućenjivati sa eksplozijom

676
00:33:28,880 --> 00:33:30,800
 slično nuklearno katastrofom,

677
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:32,700
 kao što se već ima to iskustvo

678
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:34,280
 ili vrlo bitno u memoriji

679
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:35,600
 od Černobila

680
00:33:35,600 --> 00:33:39,140
 i katastrofe Černobilske nuklearno elektrane,

681
00:33:39,140 --> 00:33:41,740
 koje i dan danas se osjećaju

682
00:33:41,740 --> 00:33:42,980
 posljedice i sve ostalo.

683
00:33:42,980 --> 00:33:45,260
 E, to je njihov bio cilj.

684
00:33:45,260 --> 00:33:46,780
 Ali nisu došli do nuklearno?

685
00:33:46,780 --> 00:33:47,940
 Nisu, e, sad nijedno.

686
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:50,240
 Dakle, rekli smo pojam, dragi gledatelji,

687
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:52,660
 to je hipermodularna struktura,

688
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:54,760
 hiperrealno vrijeme

689
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:58,480
 i hiperintegrirano bojište

690
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,940
 uz umjetnu inteligenciju.

691
00:34:00,120 --> 00:34:01,060
 Najme, o čemu se radi?

692
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:03,200
 18. godine, 2018.

693
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:05,060
 U Ministarstvu obrane,

694
00:34:05,060 --> 00:34:06,160
 tada je bio ministar

695
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:09,060
 Damir Krstičević, general,

696
00:34:09,060 --> 00:34:10,860
 on je koji sam bio našelj glavno stožar,

697
00:34:10,860 --> 00:34:11,940
 on bio moj zamjenik,

698
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:14,020
 bio zapovednik četvrte bigrade,

699
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:15,100
 prošli smo cijeli rat.

700
00:34:15,100 --> 00:34:17,440
 I onda šel za ministra

701
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,260
 i ja sam održao

702
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:20,540
 tri, četiri predavanja

703
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:21,740
 za generale

704
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:23,260
 i visoke dužnosti

705
00:34:23,260 --> 00:34:24,180
 i ministarstva.

706
00:34:24,180 --> 00:34:25,900
 I tada sam im govorio

707
00:34:25,900 --> 00:34:29,000
 da će vrlo brzo doći vrijeme

708
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:31,020
 hipermodularne,

709
00:34:31,020 --> 00:34:32,480
 odnosno modularne strukture,

710
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,900
 hipermodularne strukture

711
00:34:33,900 --> 00:34:34,980
 snaga

712
00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:37,640
 koja će biti takve

713
00:34:37,640 --> 00:34:38,700
 da će desetina,

714
00:34:38,700 --> 00:34:39,700
 12, 13,

715
00:34:39,700 --> 00:34:41,860
 a to je biblijska brojka

716
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:43,600
 12 apostola i krist,

717
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:46,220
 imati veću projekciju moći.

718
00:34:46,220 --> 00:34:48,180
 Dakle, ta skupina, desetina,

719
00:34:48,180 --> 00:34:50,260
 imat će veću projekciju moći

720
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:51,480
 nego što sada ima

721
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:52,020
 bojna.

722
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:54,640
 A bojna ima od 500 do 600,

723
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:55,920
 čak i neka i 700

724
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,300
 vojnika.

725
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:59,000
 To je modernizacija ratovanja.

726
00:34:59,000 --> 00:34:59,600
 Tako je.

727
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,320
 Ta je novog.

728
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,820
 I da će doći novog i ostalog.

729
00:35:01,820 --> 00:35:02,280
 Dobro,

730
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:04,280
 ljudi su me

731
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,860
 neki gledali,

732
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:06,680
 dobro,

733
00:35:06,680 --> 00:35:08,040
 neki su se interesirali,

734
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,180
 svi su oni zainteresirali,

735
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:09,980
 ali neki ono ovako,

736
00:35:09,980 --> 00:35:10,320
 evo,

737
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,520
 admiral pliča,

738
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,600
 koješta,

739
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:13,340
 naša otprilike.

740
00:35:13,340 --> 00:35:15,800
 I sada se mi vratimo

741
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:16,100
 ovome.

742
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:17,180
 Dakle, oni su stvorili

743
00:35:17,180 --> 00:35:18,900
 ovu hipermodularnu strukturu.

744
00:35:18,900 --> 00:35:21,220
 Desetak, čak tri su

745
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:22,140
 bila negdje vojni,

746
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:23,380
 ali su izvednici.

747
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:25,280
 Izvednici od diverzanske.

748
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,400
 I što su oni napravili?

749
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:28,540
 Uvježbali ih.

750
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:31,360
 Oni su negdje oko

751
00:35:31,360 --> 00:35:32,300
 20.000

752
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:33,500
 ukupno snaga imali,

753
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:34,300
 koja su krenuli

754
00:35:34,300 --> 00:35:35,260
 u Kursku.

755
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:36,040
 Govorite o Ukrajnicima.

756
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:37,040
 napraviti o Ukrajini.

757
00:35:37,040 --> 00:35:37,860
 Govorio je na Ukrajini.

758
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:40,320
 I te male module,

759
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,700
 one su pustili u prostor.

760
00:35:41,700 --> 00:35:45,160
 Na zapadnim oklopnim vozilima,

761
00:35:45,160 --> 00:35:46,540
 znači brzo prohodnim.

762
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:51,060
 I zapovjeđeno ime.

763
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:52,980
 Čak i jedan od tih zapovjednika,

764
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:54,080
 koje ga su zarobili,

765
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:54,860
 Rusi priča,

766
00:35:54,860 --> 00:35:56,640
 ovo čemu sad ja ću reći,

767
00:35:56,640 --> 00:35:58,180
 ali prije sam to napisao

768
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:58,720
 u svojom knjizi,

769
00:35:58,720 --> 00:35:59,200
 suvremeno,

770
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:00,400
 umijeće ratovanja,

771
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,100
 koja će izići

772
00:36:01,100 --> 00:36:01,920
 nakon ove knjige

773
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:04,220
 Uzvišena civilizacija

774
00:36:04,220 --> 00:36:05,500
 o Ilirime i Igle Goljice,

775
00:36:05,500 --> 00:36:10,220
 da ne smiju stupiti

776
00:36:10,220 --> 00:36:11,380
 u borbeni kontakt.

777
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:12,200
 Znači,

778
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:14,360
 on ima informaciju

779
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:17,480
 gdje ima zapadne satelite,

780
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,000
 uključujući i maska,

781
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,720
 ima neprekidnu mrežu.

782
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,020
 Sad je ovo pojam mreže,

783
00:36:22,020 --> 00:36:22,840
 to je sad pitno.

784
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:25,220
 Ima mrežu gdje je neprekidno

785
00:36:25,220 --> 00:36:26,600
 u realnom vremenu,

786
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:28,280
 odnosno u kiperrealnom vrijeme,

787
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,780
 a kiperrealno vrijeme je nula.

788
00:36:30,860 --> 00:36:32,360
 U vojnom umijeću

789
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,740
 realno vrijeme može biti

790
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:35,120
 jedan sat pomaknut.

791
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:36,620
 Ali je realno vrijeme,

792
00:36:36,620 --> 00:36:37,240
 jer može brzo,

793
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:38,180
 jer je glavni,

794
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:40,140
 jer to je rat četvrte dimenzije,

795
00:36:40,140 --> 00:36:41,140
 jer je to,

796
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:43,320
 a glavni geslo,

797
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:44,820
 to ga je otkri,

798
00:36:44,820 --> 00:36:45,880
 odluči i uništi.

799
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:47,540
 Dakle, vrlo brzo odjedno.

800
00:36:47,540 --> 00:36:48,080
 Sada.

801
00:36:48,080 --> 00:36:49,060
 Sada, e.

802
00:36:49,060 --> 00:36:50,740
 I to može do sat vremena,

803
00:36:50,740 --> 00:36:52,140
 jer to resimo realno vrijeme.

804
00:36:52,140 --> 00:36:53,300
 Međutim, u ovome slučaju

805
00:36:53,300 --> 00:36:54,940
 se radilo o kiperrealnom vremenu

806
00:36:54,940 --> 00:36:55,840
 ili vremenu nulu.

807
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:56,800
 Naime, o čemu je riječ?

808
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,400
 Zapovjednik te desetine

809
00:36:58,400 --> 00:37:00,760
 je imao informaciju

810
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:02,700
 sa svih mogućih satelita,

811
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:03,720
 integrirani,

812
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:06,380
 u kojem siljeve i puteve

813
00:37:06,380 --> 00:37:08,060
 određuje umjetna inteligencija

814
00:37:08,060 --> 00:37:09,960
 na način po kojem

815
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,320
 kad se vozi auto,

816
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:11,800
 dajete,

817
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,900
 skreni ovdje,

818
00:37:12,900 --> 00:37:14,100
 ovdje toliko ima,

819
00:37:14,100 --> 00:37:14,960
 tako i tu.

820
00:37:15,120 --> 00:37:17,120
 I onda te veze u krivi.

821
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:18,000
 I onda te vodi kroz šume,

822
00:37:18,000 --> 00:37:18,620
 šumarke,

823
00:37:18,620 --> 00:37:19,500
 ovo i ostaloga,

824
00:37:19,500 --> 00:37:22,200
 da ti postigne što dublji proudor,

825
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:23,240
 jer oni su morali

826
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:25,260
 za sedam dana po njihovom planu

827
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:27,060
 doći do jednog plana elektranije.

828
00:37:27,060 --> 00:37:29,600
 I sad, ne samo to,

829
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:31,520
 što omoguće još jedno,

830
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:34,020
 to je jedan novi doktrinarni fenomen,

831
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:36,060
 to je fenomen hobotnici.

832
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:37,640
 Hobotnici ima krakovi,

833
00:37:37,640 --> 00:37:38,020
 tako?

834
00:37:38,020 --> 00:37:39,240
 Osam krakov.

835
00:37:39,240 --> 00:37:41,020
 I sad, svaki krak

836
00:37:41,020 --> 00:37:42,460
 ide neovisno jedno od drugoga,

837
00:37:42,460 --> 00:37:44,300
 možda raditi.

838
00:37:44,300 --> 00:37:45,080
 Tako i ovdje.

839
00:37:45,080 --> 00:37:46,880
 Nema klasičnih pravaca

840
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,460
 koji je bio glavni pravac napada,

841
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,420
 pa jedan ili dva,

842
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:50,000
 ne znam,

843
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,220
 pomoćna pravac napada.

844
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:51,560
 Ne.

845
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:53,000
 Svi su oni glavni

846
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,140
 i svi su oni pomoćni.

847
00:37:54,140 --> 00:37:55,980
 U ovisi,

848
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:57,540
 jer ga vodi umjetna inteligencija

849
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,980
 da tamo što dublje prodre

850
00:37:58,980 --> 00:38:00,280
 za što kraće vrijeme.

851
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:02,140
 Dakle, svaki taj krak

852
00:38:02,140 --> 00:38:03,340
 djelio neovisno,

853
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:04,820
 ali svi ti krakovi

854
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,700
 stvore jednu cijelinu.

855
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:08,720
 To su ta nova doktrinarna načela.

856
00:38:08,720 --> 00:38:10,460
 To su ta nova doktrinarna načela

857
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:12,600
 koju sam ja napisao u knjizi

858
00:38:12,600 --> 00:38:15,040
 i zove se Rat mreža

859
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:17,640
 ili vremena jata i rojeva.

860
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:19,480
 Znači, besplotnih letilica.

861
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:21,520
 I oni su,

862
00:38:21,520 --> 00:38:23,300
 primjenjući umjetnu inteligenciju,

863
00:38:23,300 --> 00:38:23,960
 uspjeli

864
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,940
 u prva tri dana

865
00:38:25,940 --> 00:38:27,840
 doći do negdje dubine

866
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:30,320
 30 i koji kilometar više.

867
00:38:30,320 --> 00:38:31,660
 Neki krake je čak i duže.

868
00:38:31,660 --> 00:38:33,300
 Došao do 40 kilometara,

869
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:35,200
 ali nije došao do 70.

870
00:38:35,200 --> 00:38:36,880
 A zašto nisu uspjeli?

871
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,100
 E, zato, jer je to mreža.

872
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,880
 što se, o čemu se ovdje rade fenomen.

873
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,940
 Dakle, nema više velikih pozrobi,

874
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:45,020
 nego se te mali moduli,

875
00:38:45,020 --> 00:38:46,660
 zato se zove hipermodularna,

876
00:38:46,660 --> 00:38:48,740
 rasporede što više u prostor.

877
00:38:48,740 --> 00:38:51,220
 Ako vi rasporedite ih u prostor,

878
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:53,060
 tada su oni neki oblik čvorova,

879
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:58,180
 a oni su povezani čim komunikacijama u realnom vremenu,

880
00:38:58,180 --> 00:39:00,020
 uključujući umjetnu inteligenciju,

881
00:39:00,020 --> 00:39:01,400
 i ti stvaraš mrežu.

882
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:06,220
 I sad dolazi vrijeme ratovanja mreža proti mreža.

883
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:08,680
 Rat mreža proti mreža.

884
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:10,980
 Tu mrežu možeš uništiti na dva načina.

885
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,480
 Da uništavaš ove čvorove,

886
00:39:13,260 --> 00:39:16,240
 ili da prekineš vezu između tih čvorova.

887
00:39:16,240 --> 00:39:17,900
 Odnosno, dotok komunikacije.

888
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:18,360
 Tako je.

889
00:39:18,360 --> 00:39:18,980
 Informacije.

890
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:23,080
 E sad, ako je ovdje to radila umjetna inteligencija,

891
00:39:23,080 --> 00:39:25,280
 onda sa i druge strane,

892
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:27,700
 tj. ruske, radila je umjetna inteligencija.

893
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:30,360
 Na način, ako se ovo o krakovi,

894
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:33,360
 sad ćemo mi krak jedan,

895
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:36,660
 odnosno isto dobri rezati jedan po drugi,

896
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:37,540
 zaustavljati ga.

897
00:39:37,540 --> 00:39:40,800
 Znači, opet imaš s druge strane mrežu,

898
00:39:40,800 --> 00:39:42,300
 opet sateliti ruski,

899
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:43,820
 sve umjetna inteligencija.

900
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:44,860
 I čega sad?

901
00:39:44,860 --> 00:39:46,100
 Rusi stvaraju mrežu.

902
00:39:46,100 --> 00:39:48,820
 Rusi nisu odmah u početku stvarali mrežu,

903
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:49,820
 jer nije bilo potrebno.

904
00:39:49,820 --> 00:39:53,120
 Od ljudi, modula, hipermodula,

905
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:54,420
 oni će to kasnije uvesti.

906
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:56,700
 Sada za čišćenju proti napad,

907
00:39:56,700 --> 00:39:58,680
 proti kontraofenzivi.

908
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:00,720
 Nego su to radili

