 jer je

2612
01:34:24,000 --> 01:34:24,860
 54. godine,

2613
01:34:24,860 --> 01:34:25,560
 1000 godina

2614
01:34:25,560 --> 01:34:25,880
 od

2615
01:34:25,880 --> 01:34:27,620
 Crkvenog Raskova.

2616
01:34:27,620 --> 01:34:28,540
 Od Šizme.

2617
01:34:28,540 --> 01:34:29,540
 Tako,

2618
01:34:29,540 --> 01:34:30,300
 dakle,

2619
01:34:30,300 --> 01:34:31,060
 svijet će do tada

2620
01:34:31,060 --> 01:34:32,000
 se promijeniti

2621
01:34:32,000 --> 01:34:32,600
 i ipak će,

2622
01:34:32,600 --> 01:34:33,280
 zato je,

2623
01:34:33,280 --> 01:34:33,800
 rekao se,

2624
01:34:33,800 --> 01:34:35,220
 biće nade ima.

2625
01:34:35,220 --> 01:34:37,300
 Evropa prvo da se vrati,

2626
01:34:37,300 --> 01:34:39,020
 ono što je

2627
01:34:39,020 --> 01:34:40,320
 svijetac Ivan Pao drugi

2628
01:34:40,320 --> 01:34:40,760
 rekao,

2629
01:34:40,760 --> 01:34:41,980
 Evropo ponovo

2630
01:34:41,980 --> 01:34:43,060
 otvori vrata

2631
01:34:43,060 --> 01:34:43,660
 Kristu,

2632
01:34:43,660 --> 01:34:44,660
 odnosno

2633
01:34:44,660 --> 01:34:45,560
 lijevo i desno

2634
01:34:45,560 --> 01:34:46,360
 klušno krilo,

2635
01:34:46,360 --> 01:34:47,120
 a lijevo i desno

2636
01:34:47,120 --> 01:34:47,800
 klušno krilo,

2637
01:34:47,800 --> 01:34:48,620
 to su katolici

2638
01:34:48,620 --> 01:34:49,280
 pravstavni.

2639
01:34:50,400 --> 01:34:52,160
 ne da se mijenje,

2640
01:34:52,160 --> 01:34:52,820
 ne treba mijeniti,

2641
01:34:52,820 --> 01:34:53,920
 jer je bogaslo liturgije

2642
01:34:53,920 --> 01:34:54,620
 jedne i druge

2643
01:34:54,620 --> 01:34:55,700
 i tako dalje,

2644
01:34:55,700 --> 01:34:56,900
 ali će kršćanstvo,

2645
01:34:56,900 --> 01:34:57,740
 ali će vidite,

2646
01:34:57,740 --> 01:34:58,780
 to će kršćanstvo

2647
01:34:58,780 --> 01:35:00,340
 nastati od ove crte,

2648
01:35:00,340 --> 01:35:01,380
 Baltik,

2649
01:35:01,380 --> 01:35:01,780
 Jadran,

2650
01:35:01,780 --> 01:35:03,080
 pa sve istočno.

2651
01:35:03,080 --> 01:35:04,920
 To je ta nova civilizacija

2652
01:35:04,920 --> 01:35:05,620
 o kojoj ona govori,

2653
01:35:05,620 --> 01:35:06,140
 stepsko,

2654
01:35:06,140 --> 01:35:07,420
 Adriatska civilizacija.

2655
01:35:08,420 --> 01:35:08,840
 Dakle,

2656
01:35:08,840 --> 01:35:09,860
 ima nade,

2657
01:35:09,860 --> 01:35:12,060
 proces će biti težak.

2658
01:35:12,060 --> 01:35:13,660
 Ono što smo mi

2659
01:35:13,660 --> 01:35:15,060
 zapad prihvatili,

2660
01:35:15,060 --> 01:35:15,920
 to smo mi došli,

2661
01:35:15,920 --> 01:35:17,120
 poručeno je tamo.

2662
01:35:17,120 --> 01:35:18,560
 Mi smo u vlasti

2663
01:35:18,560 --> 01:35:19,700
 i su paloga anđela,

2664
01:35:19,700 --> 01:35:21,320
 odnosno sljedbenika njihovih

2665
01:35:21,320 --> 01:35:23,180
 i od nas ovisi,

2666
01:35:23,180 --> 01:35:25,160
 ali nažalost moram reći ovo,

2667
01:35:25,160 --> 01:35:27,000
 već kad govorimo otvoreno,

2668
01:35:27,000 --> 01:35:29,280
 najveć je zakazala ovdje

2669
01:35:29,280 --> 01:35:31,080
 hierarkijska crkva.

2670
01:35:31,080 --> 01:35:33,160
 Biskupi, radbiskupi,

2671
01:35:33,160 --> 01:35:35,560
 relati, svi ostali,

2672
01:35:35,560 --> 01:35:37,160
 oni su satvorili se

2673
01:35:37,160 --> 01:35:38,240
 kule bijelokosne,

2674
01:35:38,420 --> 01:35:40,120
 sjede i ne gledaju

2675
01:35:40,120 --> 01:35:41,500
 što radi i čine,

2676
01:35:41,500 --> 01:35:43,020
 a da govorim što radi,

2677
01:35:43,020 --> 01:35:44,740
 onaj čini u Rim.

2678
01:35:44,740 --> 01:35:47,300
 Da, nije rekao ni A ni B

2679
01:35:47,300 --> 01:35:49,200
 oko otvaranja olimpijskih igara.

2680
01:35:49,200 --> 01:35:50,000
 Neću vam reći ništa,

2681
01:35:50,000 --> 01:35:51,500
 sad ću vam reći kad on njihov sljedbenik.

2682
01:35:51,500 --> 01:35:52,980
 Oni njihovom,

2683
01:35:52,980 --> 01:35:54,120
 prozvodili njihovu politiku.

2684
01:35:54,120 --> 01:35:56,540
 Ko poziva migrante u Evropu

2685
01:35:56,540 --> 01:35:58,760
 da promijene kršćanski tet Evrope?

2686
01:35:58,760 --> 01:35:59,040
 On.

2687
01:35:59,040 --> 01:36:00,440
 Kako je rekao sad?

2688
01:36:00,440 --> 01:36:01,900
 Ko zagovara ove,

2689
01:36:01,900 --> 01:36:03,900
 a to je devijacija

2690
01:36:03,900 --> 01:36:08,140
 u odnosu razložavanje ljudske vrste.

2691
01:36:08,420 --> 01:36:10,060
 homo sapionsa.

2692
01:36:10,060 --> 01:36:10,700
 On je daj.

2693
01:36:10,700 --> 01:36:12,580
 Prema tome oni u službi

2694
01:36:12,580 --> 01:36:13,540
 i oni su ga doveli.

2695
01:36:13,540 --> 01:36:15,640
 Ja sam imao jednu emisiju,

2696
01:36:15,640 --> 01:36:17,700
 isto to rekom podcastu,

2697
01:36:17,700 --> 01:36:18,960
 gdje sam upravo govorio o tome.

2698
01:36:18,960 --> 01:36:21,900
 Ali sad recimo iz američke izbore

2699
01:36:21,900 --> 01:36:22,440
 kaže,

2700
01:36:22,440 --> 01:36:23,400
 birajte manje zlo.

2701
01:36:24,280 --> 01:36:25,420
 E sad koje je manje zlo?

2702
01:36:25,420 --> 01:36:25,760
 Da.

2703
01:36:25,760 --> 01:36:26,980
 Ali vidiš,

2704
01:36:26,980 --> 01:36:29,440
 zamisli ti duhovni vođe,

2705
01:36:29,440 --> 01:36:30,400
 katovi će oga svijeta.

2706
01:36:30,400 --> 01:36:31,280
 Birajte manje zlo.

2707
01:36:31,280 --> 01:36:31,980
 On govori da,

2708
01:36:31,980 --> 01:36:32,880
 e, ne prišli,

2709
01:36:32,880 --> 01:36:33,980
 on kaže biraj dobro.

2710
01:36:33,980 --> 01:36:34,280
 Da.

2711
01:36:34,280 --> 01:36:35,580
 Nego binjaj manje zlo.

2712
01:36:35,580 --> 01:36:37,560
 E to je ta igra okuljegarke.

2713
01:36:37,560 --> 01:36:38,060
 Inverzija.

2714
01:36:38,060 --> 01:36:38,840
 Inverzija, da.

2715
01:36:38,840 --> 01:36:39,880
 To je uopšte,

2716
01:36:39,880 --> 01:36:40,560
 ako ima zlo,

2717
01:36:40,560 --> 01:36:41,040
 dakle,

2718
01:36:41,040 --> 01:36:42,800
 mi smo ispostavili sve zlo,

2719
01:36:42,800 --> 01:36:44,140
 a ti imaš izbor,

2720
01:36:44,140 --> 01:36:45,540
 ali izbor je takav da,

2721
01:36:45,540 --> 01:36:46,100
 ako hoćeš,

2722
01:36:46,100 --> 01:36:47,280
 možeš izabrati manje zlo.

2723
01:36:47,480 --> 01:36:48,320
 Ali biraš zlo.

2724
01:36:48,320 --> 01:36:50,320
 Da, zlo je zlo.

2725
01:36:50,320 --> 01:36:52,100
 Ajde, razovimo riječi

2726
01:36:52,100 --> 01:36:52,700
 koji je na stolu,

2727
01:36:52,700 --> 01:36:53,340
 na trpezi,

2728
01:36:53,340 --> 01:36:54,960
 nema dobra.

2729
01:36:54,960 --> 01:36:56,680
 Ne da ti gira,

2730
01:36:56,680 --> 01:36:58,320
 ajde, ako im daš dvojbu,

2731
01:36:58,320 --> 01:36:59,700
 daj mi između dobra i zla.

2732
01:36:59,700 --> 01:37:02,820
 E, a Krist je to rekao.

2733
01:37:02,820 --> 01:37:04,320
 E, zato oni idu proti Krista.

2734
01:37:04,320 --> 01:37:06,820
 Krist je najveći asimetrični ratnik.

2735
01:37:06,820 --> 01:37:10,820
 On je rekao,

2736
01:37:10,820 --> 01:37:11,680
 uzmi i ostavim.

2737
01:37:11,680 --> 01:37:13,300
 Krist nikome ništa nije nudio.

2738
01:37:13,300 --> 01:37:14,900
 Od tebe ovisi što je.

2739
01:37:14,900 --> 01:37:15,480
 Dakle, biraš.

2740
01:37:15,480 --> 01:37:17,100
 I ćeš izabrati mene

2741
01:37:17,100 --> 01:37:17,680
 i moj put,

2742
01:37:17,680 --> 01:37:18,780
 ja sam istina put i živa,

2743
01:37:18,780 --> 01:37:21,340
 što piše u Ivanom evanđelju.

2744
01:37:21,340 --> 01:37:22,860
 Ili ćeš izabrati

2745
01:37:22,860 --> 01:37:24,520
 Antikrista,

2746
01:37:24,520 --> 01:37:25,440
 odnosno Satonu.

2747
01:37:25,440 --> 01:37:27,140
 To je zapravo rješenje,

2748
01:37:27,140 --> 01:37:27,980
 odnosno ona nada,

2749
01:37:27,980 --> 01:37:29,560
 a to ćemo samo pred kraj

2750
01:37:29,560 --> 01:37:31,140
 već vašu poruku dati

2751
01:37:31,140 --> 01:37:32,060
 našim gledateljima,

2752
01:37:32,060 --> 01:37:32,620
 jer rekli ste

2753
01:37:32,620 --> 01:37:34,020
 ne treba biti crno.

2754
01:37:34,020 --> 01:37:36,100
 Ne smije biti crno.

2755
01:37:36,100 --> 01:37:37,640
 Ne, da su teška,

2756
01:37:37,640 --> 01:37:38,600
 teška su vremena.

2757
01:37:38,600 --> 01:37:39,240
 Olovna vremena.

2758
01:37:39,240 --> 01:37:40,260
 Da je vrijeme velike

2759
01:37:40,260 --> 01:37:42,740
 tehtonskih poremećaja

2760
01:37:42,740 --> 01:37:45,520
 kakvih možda nisu bili

2761
01:37:45,520 --> 01:37:46,720
 povijest ljudskog roda,

2762
01:37:46,720 --> 01:37:47,720
 ali bilo ih je.

2763
01:37:47,720 --> 01:37:49,300
 Ali možda ne nedavno.

2764
01:37:49,300 --> 01:37:50,000
 Nemamo mojih,

2765
01:37:50,000 --> 01:37:50,740
 mislim da je sad,

2766
01:37:50,740 --> 01:37:51,740
 sad su ovo samo teško.

2767
01:37:51,740 --> 01:37:52,820
 Ona je izuzetno teška,

2768
01:37:52,820 --> 01:37:53,660
 ali ovdje su teška

2769
01:37:53,660 --> 01:37:55,120
 iz jednog dodatno teškoga,

2770
01:37:55,120 --> 01:37:58,140
 što je Sotona ima oružje

2771
01:37:58,140 --> 01:38:01,200
 koje mi nemamo.

2772
01:38:01,200 --> 01:38:03,740
 Oni imaju znanja,

2773
01:38:03,740 --> 01:38:06,140
 jer su oni kroz obrazani sustav

2774
01:38:06,140 --> 01:38:08,020
 uništili nama znanja,

2775
01:38:08,020 --> 01:38:08,620
 jer me uđimo,

2776
01:38:08,620 --> 01:38:10,140
 ja sam samo na primjeru

2777
01:38:10,140 --> 01:38:12,420
 ove glagoljice i ploče,

2778
01:38:12,420 --> 01:38:12,940
 rekao,

2779
01:38:12,940 --> 01:38:14,960
 i Slavena,

2780
01:38:14,960 --> 01:38:16,600
 kako su oni zokrenili,

2781
01:38:16,600 --> 01:38:18,180
 ti živiš u potpuno neistini,

2782
01:38:18,180 --> 01:38:18,940
 ne znanju.

2783
01:38:18,940 --> 01:38:20,020
 Dakle,

2784
01:38:20,020 --> 01:38:20,960
 oni imaju to,

2785
01:38:20,960 --> 01:38:23,060
 oni imaju strašno oružje,

2786
01:38:23,060 --> 01:38:24,140
 to je mediji,

2787
01:38:24,140 --> 01:38:25,580
 gdje mogu,

2788
01:38:25,580 --> 01:38:26,360
 tehnički,

2789
01:38:26,360 --> 01:38:27,720
 tehnologijski razvili,

2790
01:38:27,720 --> 01:38:29,720
 do sadašnje umjetne inteligencije.

2791
01:38:29,720 --> 01:38:31,160
 Još o gledateljima moram reći,

2792
01:38:31,160 --> 01:38:32,740
 nije to umjetna inteligencija,

2793
01:38:32,800 --> 01:38:34,600
 inteligencija koju Bog daje u čovjeku.

2794
01:38:34,600 --> 01:38:36,520
 To je jednostavno algoritam,

2795
01:38:36,520 --> 01:38:39,100
 to nema veze sa inteligencijom,

2796
01:38:39,100 --> 01:38:40,400
 nego je to algoritam

2797
01:38:40,400 --> 01:38:42,580
 koji može sam sebi proizvoditi algoritme,

2798
01:38:42,580 --> 01:38:45,380
 da bi brzo pretraživao nešto što već ima.

2799
01:38:45,380 --> 01:38:47,380
 To je ništa i sintetizirao

2800
01:38:47,380 --> 01:38:49,520
 po nekim svojim parametrema.

2801
01:38:49,520 --> 01:38:50,900
 Dakle, radi se o algoritmu,

2802
01:38:50,900 --> 01:38:51,980
 ali eto,

2803
01:38:51,980 --> 01:38:54,040
 vrlo prijemčiva je umjetna inteligencija.

2804
01:38:54,040 --> 01:38:55,220
 Dakle,

2805
01:38:55,220 --> 01:38:57,080
 ta su vremena sada teška.

2806
01:38:57,080 --> 01:38:58,580
 Ono što se,

2807
01:38:58,580 --> 01:39:00,000
 svaka strategija,

2808
01:39:00,000 --> 01:39:02,580
 ima protu strategiju.

2809
01:39:03,180 --> 01:39:04,840
 Ako mi u domovinskom ratu

2810
01:39:04,840 --> 01:39:06,620
 nismo imali oružja,

2811
01:39:06,620 --> 01:39:07,600
 koje ima oružje?

2812
01:39:07,600 --> 01:39:08,480
 I na.

2813
01:39:08,480 --> 01:39:11,380
 Ja znam kada smo bili taj sasranak

2814
01:39:11,380 --> 01:39:12,020
 sa predsjednikom tuđima.

2815
01:39:12,020 --> 01:39:13,380
 Pa šta učiniti ono sve pat?

2816
01:39:13,380 --> 01:39:14,580
 Pa predsjedniće,

2817
01:39:14,580 --> 01:39:15,240
 koje ima oružje?

2818
01:39:15,240 --> 01:39:17,260
 Pa kako koje ima?

2819
01:39:17,260 --> 01:39:17,980
 Pa i na.

2820
01:39:17,980 --> 01:39:19,680
 Pa uzvećemo od njih.

2821
01:39:19,680 --> 01:39:21,260
 E, tako i ovdje.

2822
01:39:21,260 --> 01:39:23,180
 Sada i ovi mediji

2823
01:39:23,180 --> 01:39:25,660
 uzmemo oružje od njih.

2824
01:39:25,660 --> 01:39:28,200
 Ako se oni napravili rat mreža,

2825
01:39:28,200 --> 01:39:30,060
 napravimo i mi čvorove

2826
01:39:30,060 --> 01:39:31,380
 na tim mrežama,

2827
01:39:31,380 --> 01:39:32,660
 a to znači ovakve,

2828
01:39:32,720 --> 01:39:33,800
 alternativni mediji,

2829
01:39:33,800 --> 01:39:35,100
 u kojim će se govoriti

2830
01:39:35,100 --> 01:39:35,600
 istina.

2831
01:39:35,600 --> 01:39:39,100
 Ima puno ljudi u Hrvatskoj,

2832
01:39:39,100 --> 01:39:40,400
 u svim područjima,

2833
01:39:40,400 --> 01:39:42,060
 koje znaju govoriti

2834
01:39:42,060 --> 01:39:43,720
 na istinski način.

2835
01:39:43,720 --> 01:39:44,780
 Ja govorim sa stališta

2836
01:39:44,780 --> 01:39:46,100
 geostrategije i geopolitike

2837
01:39:46,100 --> 01:39:46,880
 i vojnog omijeća,

2838
01:39:46,880 --> 01:39:48,480
 ali ima i znastanika,

2839
01:39:48,480 --> 01:39:49,800
 ima i svih kulturnih djelatnik,

2840
01:39:49,800 --> 01:39:50,720
 ima svih mogućih

2841
01:39:50,720 --> 01:39:51,960
 koji mogu govoriti.

2842
01:39:51,960 --> 01:39:52,860
 Dakle, ima,

2843
01:39:52,860 --> 01:39:53,860
 ali ovi si od nas.

2844
01:39:53,860 --> 01:39:55,640
 E, više nema mlakih duša.

2845
01:39:56,100 --> 01:39:57,580
 Kristi je rekao da smo

2846
01:39:57,580 --> 01:40:00,280
 najgore mlake duše.

2847
01:40:00,280 --> 01:40:01,100
 E, prema tome,

2848
01:40:01,100 --> 01:40:03,060
 uzimimo od Kristovog nauka

2849
01:40:03,060 --> 01:40:04,840
 i ne budimo više mlake duše,

2850
01:40:04,840 --> 01:40:05,960
 nego krenemo se,

2851
01:40:05,960 --> 01:40:06,840
 uprostavimo se,

2852
01:40:06,840 --> 01:40:07,840
 govorimo.

2853
01:40:08,320 --> 01:40:09,500
 Ovo je misija govorenja

2854
01:40:09,500 --> 01:40:10,860
 koliko mogu sad razubjeti.

2855
01:40:10,860 --> 01:40:12,340
 Zato sam i rado pristao

2856
01:40:12,340 --> 01:40:13,480
 i došao i tako dalje,

2857
01:40:13,480 --> 01:40:14,760
 jer je vrijeme sad govoriti.

2858
01:40:14,760 --> 01:40:16,000
 I govorit ćemo i dalje.

2859
01:40:16,000 --> 01:40:17,280
 Da, kad, ako ne sad.

2860
01:40:17,280 --> 01:40:18,120
 Ako ne sad.

2861
01:40:18,120 --> 01:40:19,980
 Dobro, pa velika je sreća,

2862
01:40:19,980 --> 01:40:21,940
 znate, kad imamo te medije

2863
01:40:21,940 --> 01:40:23,560
 koji misle umjesto nas.

2864
01:40:23,560 --> 01:40:27,260
 Da, pa ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

2865
01:40:27,260 --> 01:40:28,160
 Ne moramo se mučiti

2866
01:40:28,160 --> 01:40:28,260
 s razmišljenjem.

2867
01:40:28,260 --> 01:40:29,700
 Ne, ne, čak i ovo,

2868
01:40:29,700 --> 01:40:30,520
 mislijem već su nas.

2869
01:40:30,520 --> 01:40:32,940
 Oni čak ne misliju oni

2870
01:40:32,940 --> 01:40:33,480
 misliju nas,

2871
01:40:33,480 --> 01:40:35,220
 nego oni nama ne daju misliti.

2872
01:40:35,220 --> 01:40:35,660
 Eda.

2873
01:40:36,000 --> 01:40:37,360
 Oni nama jednostavno ne daju.

2874
01:40:37,360 --> 01:40:37,960
 Da, da, zapravo sve čine

2875
01:40:37,960 --> 01:40:39,220
 da nama bude ljepše.

2876
01:40:39,220 --> 01:40:41,000
 Da, da, ja moram se malo šalim.

2877
01:40:41,000 --> 01:40:41,020
 Da, da, ja moram se malo šalim.

2878
01:40:41,020 --> 01:40:44,960
 Admirale, htjela sam vas

2879
01:40:44,960 --> 01:40:45,760
 još nešto pitati.

2880
01:40:45,760 --> 01:40:46,780
 Malo prije smo spomenuli

2881
01:40:46,780 --> 01:40:48,660
 BRICS i mogućnost.

2882
01:40:48,660 --> 01:40:50,640
 Putin je pozvao tamo

2883
01:40:50,640 --> 01:40:51,620
 Aleksandra Vučića,

2884
01:40:51,620 --> 01:40:52,420
 odnosno Srbiju.

2885
01:40:52,420 --> 01:40:53,820
 Nas niko nikud ne zove.

2886
01:40:53,820 --> 01:40:55,840
 U Srbiju stalno neko nešto ide.

2887
01:40:55,840 --> 01:40:57,640
 Makoliko se mi kao rugali

2888
01:40:57,640 --> 01:40:58,740
 tim Srbima.

2889
01:40:58,740 --> 01:41:00,440
 Ispada da je najprije Vučić

2890
01:41:00,440 --> 01:41:01,900
 rekao Putinu njet,

2891
01:41:02,260 --> 01:41:03,880
 neće tamo u BRICS.

2892
01:41:03,880 --> 01:41:05,060
 A onda sad malo nešto.

2893
01:41:05,060 --> 01:41:06,760
 A jo, imam gužu užas na Istercu.

2894
01:41:06,760 --> 01:41:07,660
 Što vi mislite?

2895
01:41:07,660 --> 01:41:09,160
 Što će biti sa tom Srbijom i BRICS-om?

2896
01:41:09,160 --> 01:41:10,440
 Ova, gdje smo lijepo rekli

2897
01:41:10,440 --> 01:41:11,560
 jednom iz svi trenutka

2898
01:41:11,560 --> 01:41:13,240
 da Plejković i Vučić služi

2899
01:41:13,240 --> 01:41:14,260
 iz toga šefu.

2900
01:41:14,260 --> 01:41:14,580
 Evo ga.

2901
01:41:14,580 --> 01:41:15,760
 Ko što je služio,

2902
01:41:15,760 --> 01:41:17,180
 da gledam kao što je

2903
01:41:17,180 --> 01:41:19,720
 Pavelić i ti to slušili

2904
01:41:19,720 --> 01:41:20,820
 iz toga šefa.

2905
01:41:20,820 --> 01:41:21,860
 Evo, tako da smo...

2906
01:41:21,860 --> 01:41:22,980
 Ne da u Bog to reči.

2907
01:41:22,980 --> 01:41:25,320
 Ovaj šef bio u Londonu

2908
01:41:25,320 --> 01:41:26,640
 tada u to vrijeme,

2909
01:41:26,640 --> 01:41:28,000
 a ovaj šef je u Briselu.

2910
01:41:28,000 --> 01:41:29,880
 Evo, da se odmah razume.

2911
01:41:29,880 --> 01:41:31,260
 Srbi ko Srbi.

2912
01:41:31,260 --> 01:41:32,600
 Vučić ko Vučić.

2913
01:41:32,600 --> 01:41:33,740
 On je,

2914
01:41:33,740 --> 01:41:35,720
 to je jedna tragična figura.

2915
01:41:35,720 --> 01:41:36,720
 Ja ne znaš nešto,

2916
01:41:36,780 --> 01:41:37,700
 mi uopće njemu davamo

2917
01:41:37,700 --> 01:41:38,840
 neko posebno značenje.

2918
01:41:38,840 --> 01:41:39,780
 Ja stoji sa Srba,

2919
01:41:39,780 --> 01:41:41,280
 rekao ovako u razgovorima

2920
01:41:41,280 --> 01:41:41,600
 i ostalo.

2921
01:41:41,600 --> 01:41:44,740
 Pa da, što mu uopće dajde?

2922
01:41:44,740 --> 01:41:46,140
 Pa on je pristao.

2923
01:41:46,140 --> 01:41:48,100
 Samo ne smije obznaniti

2924
01:41:48,100 --> 01:41:50,900
 da samostalnost Kosova.

2925
01:41:50,900 --> 01:41:52,540
 A samostalnost Kosova znači

2926
01:41:52,540 --> 01:41:53,720
 stvaranje Velike Albanije.

2927
01:41:53,720 --> 01:41:55,340
 Jer je to plan ameriški.

2928
01:41:55,340 --> 01:41:56,900
 I sad on lavitira.

2929
01:41:56,900 --> 01:41:58,860
 Ima kako Srbija,

2930
01:41:58,860 --> 01:41:59,880
 to je izišlo vani,

2931
01:41:59,880 --> 01:42:00,900
 daje oružje Ukrajinu,

2932
01:42:00,900 --> 01:42:03,140
 ko što smo i mi davali.

2933
01:42:03,140 --> 01:42:04,240
 Znači kakva je razlika

2934
01:42:04,240 --> 01:42:05,540
 između politike Srbije

2935
01:42:05,540 --> 01:42:06,480
 i politike Hrvatske.

2936
01:42:06,480 --> 01:42:06,860
 Nema.

2937
01:42:06,860 --> 01:42:09,060
 I mi i oni daju oružje.

2938
01:42:09,060 --> 01:42:10,560
 Odnosno, mi još dajemo nos.

2939
01:42:10,560 --> 01:42:11,960
 On vjerojatno nije dao

2940
01:42:11,960 --> 01:42:12,820
 200 milijuna.

2941
01:42:12,820 --> 01:42:15,020
 A eto, naš Plenković je dao

2942
01:42:15,020 --> 01:42:15,500
 200 milijuna.

2943
01:42:15,500 --> 01:42:16,820
 Dobro, mi smo bogati.

2944
01:42:16,820 --> 01:42:18,860
 Ne, ne, ne, mi smo u šire duše.

2945
01:42:18,860 --> 01:42:19,780
 Mi smo, evo, tako je.

2946
01:42:19,780 --> 01:42:20,780
 I ostalo ga.

2947
01:42:20,780 --> 01:42:24,660
 I onda on, vjerojatno prvo je rekao da neće,

2948
01:42:24,660 --> 01:42:26,600
 jer mu je to trebalo iz Brisila.

2949
01:42:26,600 --> 01:42:28,960
 Onda su ovi vjerojatno mu rekli,

2950
01:42:28,960 --> 01:42:30,500
 u Srbiji, Rima tamo.

2951
01:42:30,500 --> 01:42:32,760
 Mi su oni rekli mu, slušaj,

2952
01:42:32,760 --> 01:42:33,760
 jer su već im to rekli,

2953
01:42:33,760 --> 01:42:34,400
 ovo što ću reći.

2954
01:42:34,400 --> 01:42:35,660
 Vučiću, znaš,

2955
01:42:35,660 --> 01:42:36,800
 ako ti to uradiš,

2956
01:42:36,800 --> 01:42:38,820
 odnosno, za Kosovu,

2957
01:42:38,820 --> 01:42:40,060
 a u ovom slučaju smo rekli,

2958
01:42:40,060 --> 01:42:40,800
 slušaj Vučiću,

2959
01:42:41,120 --> 01:42:42,020
 Ako ti ne ideš tamo,

2960
01:42:42,020 --> 01:42:43,320
 sveće ćete dogoreti.

2961
01:42:43,320 --> 01:42:46,520
 Dakle, kod njih nema igre.

2962
01:42:46,520 --> 01:42:52,020
 I onda je on sklon takvim perturbacijama,

2963
01:42:52,020 --> 01:42:54,340
 jer je vezan.

2964
01:42:54,340 --> 01:42:56,500
 On je prodao dušu džavolu.

2965
01:42:56,500 --> 01:42:58,180
 Evo, jednostavno rečeno.

2966
01:42:58,180 --> 01:43:00,220
 I onda on samo hoće spasti,

2967
01:43:00,220 --> 01:43:02,720
 ali duši jer je nema,

2968
01:43:02,720 --> 01:43:04,820
 jer im je džavol rada njegovom dušom,

2969
01:43:04,820 --> 01:43:06,620
 svakom ko prodao dušu džavolu,

2970
01:43:06,620 --> 01:43:09,120
 da ne govorim i kod nas to,

2971
01:43:09,120 --> 01:43:10,500
 neću, ajde, sad naše,

2972
01:43:10,500 --> 01:43:11,820
 ne smijem toliko kao admiral

2973
01:43:11,820 --> 01:43:12,940
 i bivši način glavništva,

2974
01:43:12,940 --> 01:43:14,100
 želim na takav način govoriti.

2975
01:43:14,100 --> 01:43:16,280
 I to je njegova sada politika.

2976
01:43:16,280 --> 01:43:17,880
 To je, dakle, politika bez politike,

2977
01:43:17,880 --> 01:43:18,380
 jednostavno.

2978
01:43:18,380 --> 01:43:18,860
 Sve jasno.

2979
01:43:18,860 --> 01:43:20,660
 Ali svejedno, evo, za kraj,

2980
01:43:20,660 --> 01:43:23,640
 Šefcije je nedavno naglo bio u Sarajevu,

2981
01:43:23,640 --> 01:43:24,620
 pa je otišao u Belgrad,

2982
01:43:24,620 --> 01:43:25,700
 Zagreba vidio nije,

2983
01:43:25,700 --> 01:43:27,080
 a mi smo kao neki partneri.

2984
01:43:27,080 --> 01:43:30,280
 Pa on hoće, šta će on partnere?

2985
01:43:30,280 --> 01:43:31,520
 Nikakvi mi nismo partnere,

2986
01:43:31,520 --> 01:43:32,420
 mi smo poslušnice,

2987
01:43:32,420 --> 01:43:33,540
 šta će on raditi kod nas?

2988
01:43:33,960 --> 01:43:35,600
 Jer mi slušamo što kažu.

2989
01:43:35,600 --> 01:43:37,060
 A što je onda išao u Bosnu?

2990
01:43:37,060 --> 01:43:39,160
 Pa išao u Jugoslaviju obavljati.

2991
01:43:39,160 --> 01:43:41,460
 Pa to je ovo što mu govorimo u Jugoslaviju.

2992
01:43:41,460 --> 01:43:42,540
 Jer to je sve isto vrijeme

2993
01:43:42,540 --> 01:43:45,800
 kad ovi imaju kulturne izričaje,

2994
01:43:45,800 --> 01:43:47,760
 šustrat na tromeđi.

2995
01:43:47,760 --> 01:43:49,320
 E kada se,

2996
01:43:49,320 --> 01:43:50,680
 ovaj,

2997
01:43:50,680 --> 01:43:52,080
 bijelo dugme

2998
01:43:52,080 --> 01:43:54,420
 Jugoslavijsku zastavu izvijezdu.

2999
01:43:54,420 --> 01:43:55,940
 Pa to su te iste priče.

3000
01:43:56,480 --> 01:43:58,040
 E vidiš,

3001
01:43:58,040 --> 01:43:59,000
 to je strategija

3002
01:43:59,000 --> 01:44:01,180
 kada ti posložiš

3003
01:44:01,180 --> 01:44:02,500
 u istu priču,

3004
01:44:02,500 --> 01:44:04,080
 to je strategija,

3005
01:44:04,080 --> 01:44:04,680
 obuhvatno,

3006
01:44:04,680 --> 01:44:05,820
 jer je s obuhvatno,

3007
01:44:05,820 --> 01:44:08,080
 događaje koje su razbacali

3008
01:44:08,080 --> 01:44:10,120
 ili događaje koje su pomaknuti

3009
01:44:10,120 --> 01:44:10,960
 u vremenima,

3010
01:44:10,960 --> 01:44:13,000
 pa i tišću godina.

3011
01:44:13,000 --> 01:44:14,580
 Dakle, to dio iste priče.

3012
01:44:14,580 --> 01:44:17,340
 Jer je najbolje njima bilo spriječiti,

3013
01:44:17,340 --> 01:44:19,200
 jer sada nakon

3014
01:44:19,200 --> 01:44:21,800
 ruske pobjede u Ukrajini,

3015
01:44:21,800 --> 01:44:23,740
 sad je Rusija ide projekciju

3016
01:44:23,740 --> 01:44:24,340
 svoje moći

3017
01:44:24,340 --> 01:44:26,680
 na sredinu sredozemlje.

3018
01:44:26,680 --> 01:44:27,460
 A što mislite?

3019
01:44:27,460 --> 01:44:28,040
 Gdje će srati put?

3020
01:44:28,040 --> 01:44:30,200
 Sredinu sredna progresija moći.

3021
01:44:30,200 --> 01:44:31,500
 Ne samo vojne,

3022
01:44:31,500 --> 01:44:32,880
 nego sve druge moći,

3023
01:44:32,880 --> 01:44:33,560
