3048
01:45:11,620 --> 01:45:12,720
 Ono što je bio

3049
01:45:12,720 --> 01:45:13,600
 Varsavski ugovor,

3050
01:45:13,600 --> 01:45:14,380
 to je...

3051
01:45:14,380 --> 01:45:16,040
 Opet, sad ćemo opet krivo

3052
01:45:16,040 --> 01:45:17,100
