3053
01:45:17,100 --> 01:45:17,640
 Ne, ne, ne.

3054
01:45:17,640 --> 01:45:19,740
 Samo neka ljudi razmišljaju.

3055
01:45:19,740 --> 01:45:20,640
 Dakle, ne, ovako.

3056
01:45:20,640 --> 01:45:23,900
 Do sada je bio jednopolarni svijet.

3057
01:45:23,900 --> 01:45:25,660
 Aglosaksonski, vlast,

3058
01:45:25,660 --> 01:45:26,460
 sto godina,

3059
01:45:26,460 --> 01:45:29,520
