3064
01:45:34,480 --> 01:45:36,000
 Dakle, oni su apsolutni gospodari.

3065
01:45:36,000 --> 01:45:37,500
 I oni su se tako ponašali.

3066
01:45:37,500 --> 01:45:39,620
 Ako si ti gospodar,

3067
01:45:39,620 --> 01:45:40,820
 znači svaku pojavu

3068
01:45:40,820 --> 01:45:41,760
 nekoga drugoga

3069
01:45:41,760 --> 01:45:42,860
 koji ti može osporiti

3070
01:45:42,860 --> 01:45:43,320
 tvoju moć,

3071
01:45:43,320 --> 01:45:44,160
 moraš ga uništiti.

3072
01:45:44,160 --> 01:45:45,420
 E sad,

3073
01:45:45,420 --> 01:45:47,540
 oni nisu predvidjeli

3074
01:45:47,540 --> 01:45:48,940
 ili bi onaj pijani jelicin,

3075
01:45:48,940 --> 01:45:50,240
 Rusija bila u koljenima,

3076
01:45:50,240 --> 01:45:51,720
 nisu predvidjeli

3077
01:45:51,720 --> 01:45:53,040
 asimetršnog ratnika

3078
01:45:53,040 --> 01:45:53,640
 koji se zove

3079
01:45:53,640 --> 01:45:54,920
 Vladimir Imanirović Putin

3080
01:45:54,920 --> 01:45:55,540
 iz pepela,

3081
01:45:55,540 --> 01:45:56,220
 kao Feniks,

3082
01:45:56,220 --> 01:45:57,960
 digao je Rusiju.

3083
01:45:57,960 --> 01:45:59,500
 Na vrh,

3084
01:45:59,500 --> 01:46:01,120
 vojno je doveo

3085
01:46:01,120 --> 01:46:02,700
 sa velikom projekcijom moći,

3086
01:46:02,700 --> 01:46:03,840
 sa kriperzvučnih oružima

3087
01:46:03,840 --> 01:46:04,780
 koje zapad još nema.

3088
01:46:04,780 --> 01:46:05,660
 I nema odgovoru na to.

3089
01:46:05,660 --> 01:46:06,940
 S druge strane,

3090
01:46:06,940 --> 01:46:08,780
 Kina je ona,

3091
01:46:08,780 --> 01:46:09,940
 a ko je otvorio Kini?

3092
01:46:09,940 --> 01:46:12,100
 Pa otvorio Kini Amerikar

3093
01:46:12,100 --> 01:46:12,680
 su mislili da će

3094
01:46:12,680 --> 01:46:14,100
 pomoću jeftine ratne snage

3095
01:46:14,100 --> 01:46:15,840
 imati ekstratne profite

3096
01:46:15,840 --> 01:46:20,260
 u vrijeme Kissingera,

3097
01:46:20,260 --> 01:46:22,300
 70. godina prošloga stoljeća.

3098
01:46:22,300 --> 01:46:23,380
 Kina napravila

3099
01:46:23,380 --> 01:46:24,300
 paralni sustav

3100
01:46:24,300 --> 01:46:26,300
 i digla svoje gospodarstvo.

3101
01:46:26,300 --> 01:46:26,760
 I pojela ih.

3102
01:46:26,760 --> 01:46:27,720
 I pojela ih.

3103
01:46:27,720 --> 01:46:29,560
 Znači, imaš vojnu silu projekcije,

3104
01:46:29,560 --> 01:46:30,440
