3118
01:46:45,780 --> 01:46:47,480
 velika batina u rukama

3119
01:46:47,480 --> 01:46:48,460
 okultne oligarkije

3120
01:46:48,460 --> 01:46:49,980
 da ona mogla tu ući

3121
01:46:49,980 --> 01:46:51,380
 gdje dijela po svijetu

3122
01:46:51,380 --> 01:46:52,380
 i uzimati

3123
01:46:52,380 --> 01:46:54,520
 izvaronosne resurse.

3124
01:46:54,520 --> 01:46:54,840
 Dakle,

3125
01:46:54,840 --> 01:46:57,500
 sad ima više polarnost svijeta.

3126
01:46:57,500 --> 01:46:59,620
 Ako ima ta tri velika tabora,

3127
01:46:59,620 --> 01:47:00,720
 to je prva razina.

3128
01:47:00,720 --> 01:47:01,340
 Dakle,

3129
01:47:01,340 --> 01:47:02,380
 Svije njamečke države,

3130
01:47:02,380 --> 01:47:03,280
 oni će i dalje biti,

3131
01:47:03,280 --> 01:47:04,780
 velosilnika koje tu dvojbe nema,

3132
01:47:04,780 --> 01:47:06,620
 biće Rusija i biće Kina.

3133
01:47:06,620 --> 01:47:08,500
 One su tri glavna igrača.

3134
01:47:08,500 --> 01:47:09,540
 I odnos između njih.

3135
01:47:09,540 --> 01:47:10,240
 Ja to pišem,

3136
01:47:10,680 --> 01:47:12,400
 između ostalo i u svojom novom knjizi

3137
01:47:12,400 --> 01:47:14,040
 piše na kraju nešto o tome.

3138
01:47:14,040 --> 01:47:15,900
 Ali sad u ovim knjigama

3139
01:47:15,900 --> 01:47:18,240
 sad to do kraja razradio.

3140
01:47:18,240 --> 01:47:20,760
 Ima druga razina,

3141
01:47:20,760 --> 01:47:22,040
 to je Indija,

3142
01:47:22,040 --> 01:47:23,820
 to je islamski svijet,

3143
01:47:23,820 --> 01:47:25,820
 odnosno točnije,

3144
01:47:25,820 --> 01:47:27,300
 islamski svijet bolje šire,

3145
01:47:27,300 --> 01:47:28,320
 to je afrički svijet

3146
01:47:28,320 --> 01:47:29,800
 i latinsko-američki svijet.

3147
01:47:29,800 --> 01:47:30,960
 Svi su oni budu.

3148
01:47:30,960 --> 01:47:31,900
 Evo vidimo,

3149
01:47:31,900 --> 01:47:32,780
 sada je Kina,

3150
01:47:32,780 --> 01:47:34,720
 u neki gospodarski forum,

3151
01:47:34,720 --> 01:47:37,940
 50 afričkih zemalja došlo je u Kinu

3152
01:47:37,940 --> 01:47:39,380
 i ovaj sad kaže milijardu

3153
01:47:39,380 --> 01:47:40,960
 joj ne zna šta će dati i ovi ostalo.

3154
01:47:40,960 --> 01:47:42,700
 A kako su dolazili ovi,

3155
01:47:42,700 --> 01:47:44,680
 a što je i dalje ona

3156
01:47:44,680 --> 01:47:47,020
 u neokolonialnom sustavu,

3157
01:47:47,020 --> 01:47:48,700
 pa su joj sad i sjeravaju vani,

3158
01:47:48,700 --> 01:47:51,340
 jer je dosta njima kolonializma

3159
01:47:51,340 --> 01:47:52,760
 ili svega što ima.

3160
01:47:52,760 --> 01:47:54,100
 Dakle, svijet se promjenjiva,

3161
01:47:54,100 --> 01:47:54,680
 tebala.

3162
01:47:55,560 --> 01:47:58,640
 Naravno da ima tih rubnih dijelova,

3163
01:47:58,640 --> 01:48:01,840
 a Hrvatska pripada tom rubnom dijelu,

3164
01:48:01,840 --> 01:48:03,960
 gdje može biti u ovome slučaju,

3165
01:48:03,960 --> 01:48:05,260
 može biti na zapadu

3166
01:48:05,260 --> 01:48:07,460
 i može biti na istoku.

3167
01:48:07,460 --> 01:48:11,080
 Ali, Hrvatska ima jednu jedinu točku

3168
01:48:11,080 --> 01:48:13,080
 u Evropi, nema ništa,

3169
01:48:13,080 --> 01:48:14,340
 zato moji dragi gledatelji,

3170
01:48:14,340 --> 01:48:15,520
 razumijete ovo čemu govorim,

3171
01:48:15,520 --> 01:48:16,480
 toga je bio svjestan

3172
01:48:16,480 --> 01:48:18,480
 naš predsjednik Tužban,

3173
01:48:18,480 --> 01:48:20,480
 pa je onda išao u sve zemlje

3174
01:48:20,480 --> 01:48:22,420
 da bi napravio Hrvatsko državu

3175
01:48:22,420 --> 01:48:23,060
 i obranio.

3176
01:48:23,060 --> 01:48:26,500
 To je takozvana četvrta gravitacijska

3177
01:48:26,500 --> 01:48:27,380
 stožena točka.

3178
01:48:27,380 --> 01:48:28,960
 Ima četiri u Evropi,

3179
01:48:28,960 --> 01:48:30,620
 zapravo sedamnaest i u svijetu ima.

3180
01:48:30,620 --> 01:48:33,020
 Toko najvišće razine je geostrategije.

3181
01:48:33,020 --> 01:48:35,200
 Ona je spoj, kopna i mora.

3182
01:48:35,200 --> 01:48:37,980
 I četiri su Evropi,

3183
01:48:37,980 --> 01:48:39,240
 La Manche, Gibratar,

3184
01:48:39,240 --> 01:48:41,640
 Bospod Danenele i Orthrad Jadran.

3185
01:48:41,640 --> 01:48:43,060
 A Jadran je dvije trećine naše.

3186
01:48:43,060 --> 01:48:45,180
 Dakle, mi se nalazimo na gravitacijsku točku.

3187
01:48:46,480 --> 01:48:48,260
 Tu se prelamaju

3188
01:48:48,260 --> 01:48:51,180
 utjecaj velikog tabora,

3189
01:48:51,180 --> 01:48:52,240
 aglosaksonskog,

3190
01:48:52,240 --> 01:48:53,540
 ili Amerike u podučnosti,

3191
01:48:53,540 --> 01:48:54,820
 i ruskog.

3192
01:48:54,820 --> 01:48:57,020
 Ali tu je i kineski,

3193
01:48:57,020 --> 01:48:59,180
 jer kineski novi put svigle

3194
01:48:59,180 --> 01:49:01,260
 ili kineska geopolitika

3195
01:49:01,260 --> 01:49:03,480
 završava u Savudrijskoj vali,

3196
01:49:03,480 --> 01:49:04,620
 u rijeci.

3197
01:49:04,620 --> 01:49:06,040
 Zato su kinezi gradili

3198
01:49:06,040 --> 01:49:07,680
 onaj most infrastrukturno.

3199
01:49:07,680 --> 01:49:09,400
 Dakle, na našem prostoru

3200
01:49:09,400 --> 01:49:12,280
 se sučeljaju sve tri velika tabora.

3201
01:49:12,280 --> 01:49:14,220
 Prema tome,

3202
01:49:14,220 --> 01:49:16,120
 isprana geopolitika Hrvatska

3203
01:49:16,120 --> 01:49:16,840
 bi bila ova.

3204
01:49:16,840 --> 01:49:19,160
 Voditi sa svima

3205
01:49:19,160 --> 01:49:19,900
 razgovore,

3206
01:49:19,900 --> 01:49:21,960
 a ne se opredijeliti

3207
01:49:21,960 --> 01:49:23,020
 za jednu stranu,

3208
01:49:23,020 --> 01:49:25,540
 jer niko vam ne može jamčiti

3209
01:49:25,540 --> 01:49:27,400
 da će ta strana

3210
01:49:27,400 --> 01:49:28,360
 za koju se opredijeli

3211
01:49:28,360 --> 01:49:29,720
 sutra u istinu biti

3212
01:49:29,720 --> 01:49:31,260
 glavni igraž.

3213
01:49:31,260 --> 01:49:32,120
 Odnosno,

3214
01:49:32,120 --> 01:49:33,340
 čak neopne.

3215
01:49:33,340 --> 01:49:34,900
 Jer svaki imperiju,

3216
01:49:34,900 --> 01:49:37,020
 kao što je rimski propao,

3217
01:49:37,020 --> 01:49:38,000
 tako će i propasti

3218
01:49:38,000 --> 01:49:39,460
 i američki imperiju.

3219
01:49:39,460 --> 01:49:40,740
 On već sad da se urušava.

3220
01:49:40,740 --> 01:49:42,300
 Ona je urušavao se

3221
01:49:42,300 --> 01:49:43,000
 dvijesta godina.

3222
01:49:43,000 --> 01:49:43,960
 ovaj će možda, recimo,

3223
01:49:43,960 --> 01:49:45,220
 50 ili 100 godina.

3224
01:49:45,220 --> 01:49:46,540
 Ali ne možete jamčiti.

3225
01:49:46,920 --> 01:49:47,480
 politika,

3226
01:49:47,480 --> 01:49:48,400
 kad se ti nalažiš

3227
01:49:48,400 --> 01:49:49,520
 na garantijskoj točki,

3228
01:49:49,520 --> 01:49:51,200
 ne smiješ se opredijeliti

3229
01:49:51,200 --> 01:49:52,020
 za jednu stranu,

3230
01:49:52,020 --> 01:49:53,180
 nego igrati sa svima.

3231
01:49:53,180 --> 01:49:54,460
 Znaš koji je to bije

3232
01:49:54,460 --> 01:49:55,140
 najpametniji?

3233
01:49:55,140 --> 01:49:56,980
 Dubrovončani,

3234
01:49:56,980 --> 01:49:57,920
 stariji,

3235
01:49:57,920 --> 01:49:58,720
 poklisari.

3236
01:49:59,520 --> 01:50:00,900
 E, sa svima dobro,

3237
01:50:00,900 --> 01:50:02,000
 ali slikim iskreno.

3238
01:50:02,000 --> 01:50:02,800
 A svoje,

3239
01:50:02,800 --> 01:50:04,300
 ali svoje radiš i vodijš.

3240
01:50:04,300 --> 01:50:05,020
 Mislim svoje.

3241
01:50:05,020 --> 01:50:06,220
 Sjajna poruka,

3242
01:50:06,220 --> 01:50:06,720
 admirale,

3243
01:50:06,720 --> 01:50:07,100
 za kraj.

3244
01:50:07,100 --> 01:50:07,740
 Nadam se da smo

3245
01:50:07,740 --> 01:50:08,920
 našim slušateljima

3246
01:50:08,920 --> 01:50:10,160
 i gledateljima

3247
01:50:10,160 --> 01:50:10,680
 prije svega

3248
01:50:10,680 --> 01:50:13,220
 utažili glad

3249
01:50:13,220 --> 01:50:14,580
 za novim informacijama,

3250
01:50:14,580 --> 01:50:16,020
 komentarima i analizama,

3251
01:50:16,020 --> 01:50:16,540
 a doista,

3252
01:50:16,540 --> 01:50:17,420
 evo,

3253
01:50:17,420 --> 01:50:18,300
 mislim da smo

3254
01:50:18,300 --> 01:50:19,740
 dosta toga dotakli.

3255
01:50:19,740 --> 01:50:21,420
 A jesmo dosta toga dotakli.

3256
01:50:21,420 --> 01:50:23,160
 Ovo ga bilo je zanimljivo

3257
01:50:23,160 --> 01:50:24,400
 nakon tako šest mjeseci.

3258
01:50:24,400 --> 01:50:24,820
 A da.

3259
01:50:24,860 --> 01:50:25,460
 bar se nadamo

3260
01:50:25,460 --> 01:50:26,800
 da nećemo još šest mjeseci

3261
01:50:26,800 --> 01:50:27,260
 cekati.

3262
01:50:27,260 --> 01:50:27,680
 Ok.

3263
01:50:27,680 --> 01:50:29,200
 Jer se procesi ubrzavaju.

3264
01:50:29,200 --> 01:50:30,480
 Procesi se ubrzavaju,

3265
01:50:30,480 --> 01:50:32,300
 a prvi pa lošo,

3266
01:50:32,300 --> 01:50:33,900
 nek bude kako treba.

3267
01:50:33,900 --> 01:50:34,600
 Može tako.

3268
01:50:34,600 --> 01:50:35,900
 Hvala vam najljepša,

3269
01:50:35,900 --> 01:50:36,320
 admirale.

3270
01:50:36,320 --> 01:50:36,640
 Hvala vam.

3271
01:50:36,640 --> 01:50:38,500
 Bio je ovo podcast Mrežnica

3272
01:50:38,500 --> 01:50:39,140
 naš gost,

3273
01:50:39,140 --> 01:50:41,060
 admiral Davor Domazet Lošo.

3274
01:50:41,060 --> 01:50:42,800
 Hvala vam svima na pozornosti.

3275
01:50:42,800 --> 01:50:43,800
 Vidimo se naravno

3276
01:50:43,800 --> 01:50:44,540
 vrlo brzo.

